Statistical collaboration with other IGO/NGO experts (UNEP-Dany Ghafari, UNWater-Stuart Warner, KBA Secretariat- Andrew Plumptre) - Contribution to deliverables production ([co-authored](https://ec.europa.eu/research/participants/documents/downloadPublic?documentIds=080166e5fb97ee8b&appId=PPGMS) and [reviewed](https://www.google.com/url?sa=i&rct=j&q=&esrc=s&source=web&cd=&cad=rja&uact=8&ved=0CDgQw7AJahcKEwjwuPDSkNeAAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQAw&url=https%3A%2F%2Fec.europa.eu%2Fresearch%2Fparticipants%2Fdocuments%2FdownloadPublic%3FdocumentIds%3D080166e5fb95b64d%26appId%3DPPGMS&psig=AOvVaw0TX6uT7L5x9hlK2PGC3wUX&ust=1691930009347562&opi=89978449)) - Course content lead: Pr. Eurostat/SDSN data analysis for the Monitoring framework and coordination mechanism for SDGs in Cyprus project ### Data Analyst - **Swiss Federal Statistical Office (FSO), Geb√§ude und Wohnungen Sektion** -*Jul. 2015 - Jun. 2016* - Specifying algorithms using PL/SQL language for external data loading - Process description in accordance with BPMN standards - Data analysis of the Federal Register of the Dwellings & Buildings for quality and comprehensiveness comparison with external data (Baublatt) - Formulation of proposals regarding the Federal Register improvement (written report) - **Glenmark Pharmaceuticals, Downstream Process team** -*Nov. 2017 - Feb. 2018* - Development of VBA Modules for database construction and data mining purposes to classify purification stages - Statistical support to Downstream Processes (DSP) scientists and engineers - **UC Rusal AG, Market Intelligence Unit** -*Jul. 2017 - Oct. 2017* - Development of VBA Modules for loading and managing CRU historical aluminum data - Construction of database based on CRU historical data (data analysis, data standardization processes) using VBA-Access from VBA-Excel - Proposal of different solutions on automation macros to update the database -
